{"tid":2038894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"孟晚舟確定送美","createTime":"2020-05-27T18:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T04:10:23.000Z","uid":118550,"like":514,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0fdd8bab5f1a993d99b35571a4503b63f971ad","tid":2038894,"uid":118550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CBCAlerts/status/1265705327279976448?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBCAlerts%2Fstatus%2F1265705327279976448%3Fs%3D19&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b3aac376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBCAlerts%2Fstatus%2F1265705327279976448%3Fs%3D19&h=bb41ef90\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CBCAlerts/status/1265705327279976448?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\nB.C. Supreme Court judge delivers major blow to Meng Wanzhou, ruling that extradition proceedings against the Huawei executive should proceed. Judge rules the offence Meng is accused of by American prosecutors would be considered a crime if it occurred in Canada.<br />\n<br />\nThe BC ruling says the essence of Meng&rsquo;s alleged crime is fraud. Meng, the 48-year-old chief financial officer of the telecommunications giant, is charged with fraud in the United States for allegedly deceiving banks into a possible violation of economic sanctions against Iran.<br />\n<br />\nThe BC court ruling on Meng Wanzhou means the proceedings and the extradition bid will proceed, but it does not mean that she will be extradited. Meng's legal team had argued that Canada doesn't have the same sanctions against Iran, so no crime had been committed.<br />\n<br />\nEnglish-language newspaper affiliated with China's communist party reacts to Meng Wanzhou ruling. Headline says 'Ruling on Meng shows Canada lost judicial, diplomatic independence to US bullying: experts'. Story calls ruling 'unjustified,' says it makes Canada a 'pathetic clown.'<br />\n<br />\n-CBC NEWS"},{"pid":"62e07e8a14d305d2a2115ce13e90c1e4c0e8ed81","tid":2038894,"uid":16959,"like":372,"dislike":2,"score":370,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:34:29.000Z","msg":"啲小粉紅唔係話會四日返到國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌唔撚記得佢係米國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2337c1ce3c868a82eda10b58230d6c47f2901585","tid":2038894,"uid":21424,"like":423,"dislike":2,"score":421,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEg9Q7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEg9Q7N.jpg&h=ce322367&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc7c5b194be84171a39133c1052a7da407fa04fa","tid":2038894,"uid":27250,"like":192,"dislike":2,"score":190,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:34:48.000Z","msg":"又多條武器，睇嚟華為都收硬皮<br />\n可以開間新公司叫習為"},{"pid":"999758825907ce4158b19bd3faeab118e28b2f98","tid":2038894,"uid":103230,"like":165,"dislike":0,"score":165,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:34:55.000Z","msg":"佢終於可以直接去美國等iphone12發佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d54419a1dbef08483d2e1713f3be9896de4f6cc","tid":2038894,"uid":20870,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"等睇棄保潛逃話美國司法不公 相信中國法治"},{"pid":"a2e693d72972bb33bd7045240dee9cdeaba5085e","tid":2038894,"uid":321837,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"62e07e8a14d305d2a2115ce13e90c1e4c0e8ed81","tid":2038894,"uid":16959,"like":372,"di